title: Will the Lakers Make a Panic Trade? Plus, Second-Guessing the Sabonis and McCollum Deals. | Group Chat
description:
Verrier, Rob, and Wos debate what can (and should) be done to solve the Lakers' problems at the deadline (1:40), before breaking down the surprising trades for Domantas Sabonis and CJ McCollum and making final predictions (18:00).
Hosts: Justin Verrier, Rob Mahoney, Wosny Lambre
Producer: Devon Manze
